{
  "stem": "26672.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know how long the ghetto was established.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But, um-- but then suddenly town was surrounded one morning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a commotion and town was surrounded.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then German lorries came in, surrounded the center of the town, and took everybody into-- into the mid-- square of the town and started transporting them to-- away.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we didn't, but my father, somehow, managed to bribe  a guard to let me through.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't remember the guards' name now.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, my father-- I remember my father coming to-- to the house, and pulling me by my hand.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said, I want you to escape, and to [INAUDIBLE] I think there should be somebody of the family left.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I will tell you where.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Make for such and such farm, and that I've given the men certain valuables and he will look after you.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he thought, obviously.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so I escaped.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES] Don't ask me how I managed to escape.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't really know how.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was, um, Germans going up and down the road.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was dressed-- I must have been dressed in the almost in the uniform that I wore with the black coat.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so I didn't look Polish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Why they didn't stop me, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then with minutes escaping a sister, my second older sister, Leah, came running and we managed-- met up with me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she managed to-- to escape with me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All I know is that the man, the farmer that I made for, my father told me to-- to go to eventually came home that night and he told me, he so.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He took a horse and cart.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were ordered to bring horse and carts to town to transport the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
